HALE COUNTY et al., Appellants, v. AMERICAN INDEMNITY COMPANY et al., Appellees. No. 6691. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Aug. 14, 1933. For former opinion, see 63 F.(2d) 275.

Before BRYAN, SIBLEY, and HUTCH-ESON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The petition for rehearing in the above numbered and entitled cause is denied.
